        <Parent_String>roofing nails [300048959], nails by location or context [300048924], nails (fasteners) [300033565], fasteners [300036363], components by general context [300241581], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
